overview: Jinguuji Nao October 2017 AV debut, which received a lot of praise already.  First of all, she looks very cute, almost like an idol. She was very nervous about doing things and appearing in camera for the first time. But gradually she was feeling more comfortable and smiling more. Then she was tagged as a virgin, and the gimmick is that she’s losing her virginity on this video.  The variety of facial expressions was great and as far as debuts go, this was really good.
title: A Virgin Graduation Her AV Debut Nao Jinguji, Age 20, Number of Sexual Partners: 0 A Tension-Filled First Time Uncut Film Session
